# ============================================================================
# .cursorignore — Intentionally Empty
# ============================================================================
# Cursor is ALLOWED to read all project files for context and understanding.
# 
# WRITE PROTECTION is handled by .cursor/rules/ files:
#   - tobi-protected-files.mdc (alwaysApply: true) — blocks writes to 60+ files
#   - tobi-flash-glob-guard.mdc (glob-triggered) — warns when viewing protected files
#
# Do NOT add Tobi's protected files here. Cursor needs to read them to
# understand the codebase, suggest correct imports, and avoid breaking
# interfaces. The rules files handle the "read OK, write BLOCKED" policy.
# ============================================================================
